Gimp python plugin

1. Create image composed of two layers: 
  * Top layer - left eye, red colour. 
  * Bottom layer - right eye, greem colour.

[2. - optional - Show 4 points using path tool:
   * first point - both layers common point on top layer - layers will be translated to cover corresponding point from bottom layer (see third point),
   * second point - fixed height point on first layer - layers will be rotated to set corresponding point from bottom layer on the same y coordinate level (see fourth point)
   * third point - both layers common point on bottom layer,
   * fourth point - fixed height point on bottom layer.]
    
3. Select "Create 3D" option from "3D Tools" menu.
   
